<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="determination-n">determination <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪˌtɜːmɪ'neɪʃn/    美 /dɪˌtɜːrmɪ'neɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 决定； 决心；果断：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>carry out the plan with determination 
坚决执行计划</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If we have the courage and determination, we will finally get the sunshine we want.  
只要有勇气和决心，我们终会得到我们想要的阳光。</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The important thing in life is to have a great aim, and <strong>the determination to</strong> attain it
人生最重要的事情是确定一个伟大的目标，并下定决心去实现它。</p><footer>——歌德</footer></div></div>